TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
$BR
For the  cost function
\(C(x)=$a+$b x + $c x^2 \) and the demand
function \( p(x) = $b3 \),
find the production level that will maximaze profit.
$BR Production Level = \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $b/$c;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

